        "mainbody": "'''Graddis''' was a [[werebear]] inhabiting [[Zhentil Keep]]'s [[Zhentil Keep/Foreign Quarter|Foreign Quarter]] during the mid-to-late 14{{th}} century [[DR]].",
        "Activities": "Graddis lived and worked with [[Tymora's Holy Hall of Good Fortune and Casino]]. He patrolled the halls of the temple, monitoring the gamblers for any signs of trouble. Graddis would change into a fearsome [[bear]] and approach troublemakers, grabbing minor offenders with his paws and hurling them outside. Serious threats were attacked with vigor and Graddis was usually aided by [[Tymora]]'s [[cleric]]s."
